{"tid":1901942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CSI口罩邊度黎?  訪問市民，4成人都說口罩在市面上買得到","createTime":"2020-02-28T05:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T06:35:25.000Z","uid":186071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b1b1ac8fc90474095fd96c8c41d3452ff5715cf","tid":1901942,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"【CSI口罩邊度黎?】<br />\n<br />\n懲教署生產的CSI口罩，限於政府使用，不能在市面出售。但《新聞刺針》發現港九新界，都有店鋪出售過CSI口罩。<br />\n<br />\n我們在街頭及網上問了超過100名有CSI口罩的市民，<br />\n大約4成人都說口罩在市面上買得到，到底他們在哪裡買呢？<br />\n<br />\n有市民指曾經在深水埗、沙田、銅鑼灣藥房購入，也有市民曾經目擊中年男子在新蒲崗街頭交收。記者一一了解過。<br />\n<br />\n#口罩 #CSI #新聞刺針<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/153300521509664/posts/1484318745074495/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F153300521509664%2Fposts%2F1484318745074495%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=845ff895\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/153300521509664/posts/1484318745074495/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"434eceb0ed340b8ae38555583205b40ade6b7e3f","tid":1901942,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:48:03.000Z","msg":"這就是8964時, 係支那國叫「官倒」既貪污行為<br />\n<br />\n「官倒」 = 低價官方資源, 高價倒賣比民間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b609f6d2654623c38b8683eb6f03231b06b1bb91","tid":1901942,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"2020年, 香港已腐化成支那國"},{"pid":"fa90cd66f56e33f0ecaacf68d63a1b41d8f336c9","tid":1901942,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b609f6d2654623c38b8683eb6f03231b06b1bb91","tid":1901942,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"2020年, 香港已腐化成支那國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"訓左冇睇，ICAC執左有幾多年??"},{"pid":"7e97f5faad49d56ac1ee06c6362b8d94f043c2bf","tid":1901942,"uid":48582,"like":0